{"tid":1814291,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實，退唔退場 又有咩所謂？","createTime":"2020-01-07T00:40:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T05:53:43.000Z","uid":172599,"like":38,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a99fd41369b229c727eebd65b1be8dcab1d2b8bc","tid":1814291,"uid":172599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T00:40:39.000Z","msg":"由一開始呢個運動既宗旨<br />\n<br />\n就係和勇不割不分<br />\n<br />\n覺得ready就上 唔ready就落<br />\n<br />\n關其他人咩事？<br />\n<br />\n如果你支持勇武，覺得少一個會少好多，問下自己，自己點解唔上<br />\n<br />\n如果你落開場既，你應該明白其他人都係人，要退場休息，無必要屌<br />\n<br />\n如果因為幾個隊退場你地就屌晒鬼，咁你地真係太睇得起勇武了<br />\n<br />\n如果係怕落場人數少左而感到憤怒害怕，你係時候問吓自己有幾願意付出了<br />\n<br />\n其實退唔退場、捉唔捉鬼，都唔係重點<br />\n<br />\n我重點係，大家唔需要咁受氣，因為<br />\n<br />\n無論結果係點，個結果都係大家一齊受<br />\n<br />\n我、你 冷氣軍師又好，勇武又好<br />\n<br />\n殊途同歸"},{"pid":"f9f984d4a03162744389fdf86b9fb2e895bedbac","tid":1814291,"uid":172599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T00:48:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4fbb8628e1e4a6c56f621050ba867f0e3d2d7136","tid":1814291,"uid":59472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T01:12:33.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"1a91a5bb8142f03cfab67c8fc130874e6daaaad2","tid":1814291,"uid":172599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T01:15:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"30ab00fc76890b8159277ce22e7753c12d513a5c","tid":1814291,"uid":172599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T01:52:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"064ce411ab8728a57013adf9a59088c6187f95a4","tid":1814291,"uid":161404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T01:59:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ecd73e7482c3e73eca4c993ec66e610e46fe83ae","tid":1814291,"uid":172599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T02:01:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9f9517a84ff0654799601980204dddc77433adff","tid":1814291,"uid":279401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T02:02:18.000Z","msg":"突發！和勇全面退場<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1814289\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1814289</a>"},{"pid":"4ab98332db572aa6f6cef23b93b3d5f09914f10d","tid":1814291,"uid":172599,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T02:04:13.000Z","msg":"提提大家，當你係一個勇武，你覺得身邊人付出少<br />\n<br />\n其實你要退一退場，因為你已經開始計較，而我地理念係不計較<br />\n<br />\n如果你係一個和理非，你見到勇武退場你就心灰，咁其實你已經心底裡覺<br />\n<br />\n得和理係無用，你亦都要反思"},{"pid":"ad005c5a235b5408405c7080fbdb061e4010b1fd","tid":1814291,"uid":172599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T02:11:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d0ea0e01fa87d2e817fd72e05e24d00ba17b78f4","tid":1814291,"uid":172599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T02:20:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ff3aa99aab6d2490d0d23c88846384a090fcaa9","tid":1814291,"uid":149877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T02:23:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a13860d3a30b1bc1ff6fbf962976fa65f74d468e","tid":1814291,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T02:28:33.000Z","msg":"和勇不分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eafdf18ef051987564cdae4213273a62d32cad23","tid":1814291,"uid":172599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T02:30:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4806665f05c3894a6f73e94db10abc3023b74c19","tid":1814291,"uid":93124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T03:09:11.000Z","msg":"[長文] 要革命，請先革了自己的命<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eJFHRS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eJFHRS</a>"},{"pid":"c4a8f5f34c7aa270c336c356faedd0337e8c9d23","tid":1814291,"uid":172599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T04:11:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2b5cd5a8985d5ed1b207bf928877074f6619bea1","tid":1814291,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T04:17:20.000Z","msg":"認同"},